@startuml
title ATM Control - Withdrawal Process

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForAmount
state ValidatingAmount
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state Dispensing
state Printing
state Ejecting
state Confiscating
state Terminating
state ClosedDown

Idle : entry / Display Welcome
ClosedDown : entry / Display System Down

Idle --> WaitingForAmount : Card Inserted / Get Amount

WaitingForAmount --> ValidatingAmount : Amount Entered / Validate Amount
WaitingForAmount --> Confiscating : Card Confiscated / display Confiscated

ValidatingAmount --> WaitingForAmount : Invalid Amount / Invalid Amount Prompt
ValidatingAmount --> Confiscating : Card Stolen, Card Expired \nConfiscate, Update Status
ValidatingAmount --> Confiscating : Third Invalid Amount \nConfiscate

ValidatingAmount --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Valid Amount / Display Menu

WaitingForAmount --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForAmount --> Confiscating : Cancel / Confiscate

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

Dispensing --> Printing : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt, Display Cash Dispensed, Confirm Cash Dispensed
Dispensing --> ClosedDown : Insufficient Cash / Eject

Printing --> Ejecting : Receipt Printed / Eject

Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected / Display Ejected
Confiscating --> Terminating : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated

Terminating --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Not Requested]
Terminating --> ClosedDown : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Was Requested]

ClosedDown --> [*] : After (Elapsed Time)

@enduml
